    "steam_appid": 1792160,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792160/extras/68e28ccb1842230af0014afa66e8b7be.avif?t=1769794475\" width=257 height=351 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SPHEROCIOUS is a short but sweet, handcrafted 2.5D puzzle platformer about a sloth and a renegade scientist saving the Amazon rainforest from a greedy logging corporation.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Who This Game is For</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fans of adventure, mystery, and dystopian comedy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792160/extras/21e3a30115f42f8818eb7878aea97538.avif?t=1769794475\" width=1560 height=780 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to Play</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crawl</strong>, <strong>jump</strong>, and <strong>roll</strong> your way through the jungle while <strong>solving ancient puzzles</strong> and <strong>battling advanced forestry bots</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time your moves strategically, because you need to manage your <strong>stamina</strong>. Every movement (<strong>crawling, jumping, inflating</strong>) uses some of your stamina, but it recharges with time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your<strong> bot</strong> assistant can <strong>launch</strong> you through the air and water or <strong>boost</strong> you on the ground, so <strong>alternate</strong> between using it and your own movement abilities to find the most efficient path forward</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take matters into your own claws </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792160/extras/21e3a30115f42f8818eb7878aea97538.avif?t=1769794475\" width=1560 height=780 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>After having underwent an experimental genetic modification process, a sloth gains sudden clarity about its habitat.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the help of a lone biologist, it harnesses a lost civilization's power source in order to uncover the truth about an invasive forestry operation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792160/extras/8160d3b5dbf7891cfbe2170a90cf5f1c.avif?t=1769794475\" width=257 height=273 /></span></p>",
